it.polito.dp2.NFFG

Interface ReachabilityPolicyReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NamedEntityReader, PolicyReader
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    TraversalPolicyReader

    public interface ReachabilityPolicyReader
extends PolicyReader
    An interface for accessing the data associated to a Reachability policy. A reachability policy specifies a property that is the existence of a path in the NF-FG that connects a source node to a destination node.
